message: Love the interface. Clean and simple. Perfect for first-time users.
Pretty straightforward. Would be nice to have more language options though.
Very easy to use! Found everything I needed quickly. Great job!
The heat map showing popular exhibits is really clever. Helped me decide what to see first!
Nice interface! My parents would love to use this too. Would it be possible to add Sinhala and Tamil language options?
Good kiosk! An audio guide feature could be a nice addition for visitors who prefer listening to reading.
Good information! When the internet was slow, some features took time to load.
Love this! My suggestion: multi-language support would help visitors who are more comfortable in Sinhala or Tamil.
